<%= form_for @device, url: {action: "create"}, html: {class: "form-group"} do |f| %>
  <%= label(:imei, "Enter IMEI", class: "control-label") %>
  <%= f.text_field(:imei, class: "form-control input-lg fifth-width", placeholder: "15 digits, no spaces") %><br>
  <%= label(:name, "Enter a friendly name", class: "control-label") %>
  <%= f.text_field(:name, class: "form-control input-lg fifth-width", placeholder: "G-RALA") %>
  <%= f.submit("Search", class: "form-control") %>
<% end %>

Since this is still in development, an IMEI and a name MUST be supplied, or an error will be raised.